data.title: Some Descendants of the PORTUGAL Family Related to George Washington 1st US President
data.text:
2. i. Alfonso III Of PORTUGAL King Of Portugal 466 467 was born 5 May 1210 in Coimbra, Portugal, died 16 Feb 1278 or 1279 in Lisbon, Portugal at age 67, and was buried in Mosterio de Alcobaca, Alcobaca, Portugal. 3. i. Diniz 'Denis' DE PORTUGAL King Of Portugal 469 470 471 was born 9 Oct 1261 in Lisbon, Portugal and died 7 Jan 1325 in Santarem, Portugal at age 63. 4. i. Alfonso IV DE PORTUGAL King of Portugal [1325-1357] 68 was born 8 Feb 1291 in Lisbon, Portugal 68 and died 28 May 1357 in Lisbon, Portugal 68 at age 66. 5. ii. Constanza Dinisez DE PORTUGAL Princess of Portugal was born 3 Jan 1290 in Lisbon, Portugal and died 17 Nov 1313 in Sahagun, Leon, Spain at age 23. 6. i. Maria Alfonsez DE PORTUGAL Princess of Portugal 68 was born about 1313 in Coimbra, Coimbra, Portugal,68 died 18 Jan 1357 in Evora, Portugal 68 about age 44, and was buried in Chapel of the Kings, Sevilla Cathedral, Sevilla, Castile, Spain. 7. ii. Pedro Affonsez I 'the Stern' DE PORTUGAL King of Portugal [1357-1367] 68 was born 18 Apr 1320 in Coimbra, Coimbra, Portugal 68 and died 18 Jan 1368 in Estremoz, Evora, Portugal 68 at age 47.

8. i. Juan Perez 'the Great' DE PORTUGAL King of Portugal [1385-1433] 68 376 was born 11 Apr 1358 in Lisbon, Portugal,68 376 died 4 Aug 1433 in Lisbon, Portugal 68 376 at age 75, and was buried in Batalha Abbey, Leiria, Portugal.68 376 9. i. Alfonzo Juanez DE PORTUGAL Duke of Braganza was born 10 Aug 1377 in Veiros, Alentejo, Portugal, died 15 Dec 1461 in Chaves, Vila Real, Portugal at age 84, and was buried in Convent San Francisco, Guimaraes, Braga, Portugal. 10. i. Juan Juanez DE PORTUGAL Prince of Portugal was born 13 Jan 1400 in Santarem, Santarem, Portugal and died 18 Oct 1442 in Alcacer do Sal, Setubal, Portugal at age 42. 11. i. Isabella Alfonza DE PORTUGAL Princess of Braganza was born about Oct 1402 in Barcellos, Braga, Portugal, died 26 Oct 1465 in Arevalo, Avila, Spain about age 63, and was buried in Mosterio de Batalha, Leiria, Portugal.
